If you create a ticket from a Website Form and your website use SMTP protocol to send emails in your JIRA Service Desk will have always *the same* *Reporter*(the webmaster email address used in SMTP protocol to send emails).

{color:#205081}So if you reply to this tickets recieved in JIRA Service Desk thru a Website Form(sent via SMTP protocol) +the Reporter are always declared incorrectly+!{color}

JIRA Service Desk declare Reporter from *To* instead use *Reply-To* path(the standard SMTP header).

h3. Summary

Previously in JIRA (v1000.892.1) when calling endpoint https://instance.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/issue/{{issuekey}} 

The return for the organization field of an issue in JIRA Service desk was:

{code}
"customfield_10001": null,
"customfield_10002": [
            "exampleorganization"
        ],
"customfield_10006": null,
{code}

In JIRA 1000.962 the response is coming with additional details

{code}
"customfield_10001": null,
"customfield_10002": [
            {
                "_links": {
                    "self": "https://instance.atlassian.net/rest/servicedeskapi/organization/1"
                },
                "id": "1",
                "name": "exampleorganization"
            }
        ],
"customfield_10006": null,
{code}

The problem is that this change was not communicated and customers using scripts expecting the old pattern now need to change their scripts in order to fully work with JIRA API.

h3. Steps to Reproduce

Call this endpoint for an issue in service desk with an organization in custom field.

# https://instance.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/issue/{{issuekey}}

h3. Expected Results

Receive the response as following

{code}
"customfield_10001": null,
"customfield_10002": [
            "exampleorganization"
        ],
"customfield_10006": null,
{code}


h3. Actual Results

Receiving the organization with 


{code}
"customfield_10001": null,
"customfield_10002": [
            {
                "_links": {
                    "self": "https://instance.atlassian.net/rest/servicedeskapi/organization/1"
                },
                "id": "1",
                "name": "exampleorganization"
            }
        ],
"customfield_10006": null,
{code}

h3.Workaround

None.
